title: Cheerio Puppy Chow
directions: Step 1 - Microwave chocolate chips, peanut butter and butter for about 1 minute.Stir in vanilla.
Step 2 - Put 8 cups of cheerios into a Tupperware bowl with a lid.
Step 3 - Pour chocolate/peanut butter mixture on top of cheerios and mix until coated well.
Step 4 - Pour confectioners sugar on top and shake well!
